vote.title: Authorize a three-year service price agreement for rental and maintenance of portable toilets for the Park & Recreation Department - United Rentals (North America), Inc. dba Reliable Onsite Services, lowest responsible bidder of two - Estimated amount of $1,914,118 - Financing:  General Fund ($1,897,056), Dallas Water Utilities Fund ($14,579), and Stormwater Drainage Management Fund ($2,483) (subject to annual appropriations)
